body:
@paulocoghi 

This was during the short period before I rebuilt the servers. So still with version 1.6.1.

And you may be better off not migrating the users: The "bad guys" added a few users. And also a few db's (with only one document each).

@ricellis good suggestions from API's point of view.
```
POST _dbs_info {"keys" : ["dbName1", "dbName2"]}
```
Ping @davisp @rnewson @mikerhodes for further comments.

If not, I can continue to change to provide above new API :-)

@jiangphcn when you merge a PR to fix a bug, please put

"Fixes #1051"

in your PR commit message, that will auto-close the issue. :)
